    "name": "Ticket Matrix API",
    "description": "Emmanuel Aro's project submission for evaluation. Full CRUD + aggregation collection for the Nativetalk ticketing module backend (Django REST Framework). Set the `base_url` collection variable to your API root (defaults to http://localhost:8000/api).",
